title: Sinnoh-Dex’s Official Art Commissions!
body:
Busts as seen above: $10 

- Full bodies as seen above: $15-20 depending on detail.
- Extra character +$3 for bust +$5 for full body.
- Will do:
  Humans, furries, OCs, canon characters, shipping art (keep it appropriate), ask about NSFW
- Will not do:
Mechs, extreme NSFW, ask if not sure.

Notes: I’m saving up to move and so I’m looking for a bit of income that I can stock away, if you’re interested you can send me an ask or a DM, I’m more than willing to work with you and most times I get to things like this pretty quickly. 

If you’re not interested in a commission yourself please REBLOG! Thank you so much.

blog.name: nanitezi
blog.title: Found Dead In Miami
blog.description:
Natalia / 20 / PuertoRican-Cuban / lover of all things fantasy and DnD.

My current fandoms include The Dragon Prince (new baby!), The Arcana, Miraculous Ladybug, The Adventure Zone, and Young Justice. I also love comic books (like Zodiac Starforce, Sleepless, Sunstone, Newprints, Moonstruck, Snotgirl, Monstress, Five Worlds, Goldie Vance), webcomics (like Satan and Me, Knight's Errant, I Love Yoo, Not Drunk Enough, Exorcism Academy, Demon House, Sharp Zero), shoujo anime/manga (like Noragami, Skip Beat, Kamisama Kiss, Ouran), books (like The Poppy War, A Discovery of Witches, Uprooted, Renegades, A Matter of Magic), and a lot more. I like a lot of things. Feel free to talk to me about them.

summary: Little redesign of my favorite titan. I saw a gif on tumblr of her and remembered how the leotard always bothered me as a kid...
caption: Little redesign of my favorite titan. I saw a gif on tumblr of her and remembered how the leotard always bothered me as a kid (as well as Star’s tankini) and also how the belt looked too flimsy and pointless so I changed it up a little. And of course she has shorts under her skirt. The attitude stays.
